review_text: Was nice, they have a piano.
Pleasant small park between a church and a school
Great place in the summer with the swings and the pretty lights. Also, they occasionally have outdoor cinema
Nice little quiet place to eat lunch outside during the right seasons and even has shelter in the eventuality of rain, very nice little gem within the area.

(Translated by Google) Much improvement this summer

(Original)
Beaucoup d'amélioration cet été

(Translated by Google) Beautiful park, with several picnic tables

(Original)
Beau parc, avec plusieurs tables de pique nique

(Translated by Google) Very beautiful with a lot of greenery and in front of a church! They put a lot of stuff for the summer too!

(Original)
Très beau avec beaucoup de verdure et devant une église! Ils mettent beaucoup de trucs pour l'été aussi!

(Translated by Google) Great, this summer there are a lot of improvements. More things to do with children and huts with swing are an exito.

(Original)
Super , cet été il y a beaucoup des améliorations. Plus de choses a faire avec les enfants et les cabanes avec les balançoire sont un éxito.

(Translated by Google) Small park with a lot of life! Two streets are blocked off in the summer to provide facilities such as picnic tables, sandbox for children, hanging swings, 4-seater swings on wheels.
Some of these facilities are covered with a roof for shade or protection in the event of rain.
There is also an enclosure for playing field hockey (Cosom).

(Original)
Petit parc avec beaucoup de vie!  Deux rues sont bloquées l'été pour y mettre des installations telles des tables de picnic, bac à sable pour les enfants, balançoires suspendues, balançoires 4 places sur roues.
Certaines de ces installations sont recouvertes d'un toit pour y faire de l'ombre ou protéger en cas de pluie.
Il ya aussi une enceinte pour y jouer au hockey gazon (Cosom).

(Translated by Google) Great in the summer there is a BBQ a piano for the public Nike picking table and parasol etc.

(Original)
Génial l'été ya un BBQ un piano pour le public table de pick nike et parasol etc

(Translated by Google) Beautiful summer carnival party

(Original)
